    pc "“能让你开心我就高兴。你肯定也还有几招没使出来吧。”"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:203
translate chinese connie15_88f76d9a:

    # con "You betcha."
    con "“那还用说。”"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:206
translate chinese connie15_bee0b92a:

    # "She takes a box of cigarettes out of her night stand and lights one up."
    "她从床头柜里拿出一包香烟，点了一根。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:207
translate chinese connie15_4fb3d9c8:

    # con "Do you want a smoke?"
    con "你要来根吗？"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:208
translate chinese connie15_cdac1b0a:

    # pc "No thanks, I don't smoke cigarettes."
    pc "不用了，谢谢，我不抽烟。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:209
translate chinese connie15_7d74ff93:

    # con "I don't really either. I think I've had this pack for a year or so."
    con "我其实也不怎么抽。这包烟大概放了一年左右了。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:212
translate chinese connie15_98da17ed:

    # con "Right now, after that, a cigarette hits just right."
    con "刚做完那事，现在来根烟正合适。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:213
translate chinese connie15_596c0f44:

    # con "You know, besides my husband, you're the first man I've had sex with in fifty years."
    con "你知道吗，除了我丈夫，你是五十年里第一个和我上床的男人。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:214
translate chinese connie15_6a75940e:

    # pc "Really? You and Jackson never had anything?"
    pc "真的吗？你和杰克逊之间从来没有发生过什么？"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:215
translate chinese connie15_03c8c55b:

    # con "Naw, he's like a brother to me. He's never looked at me like that."
    con "没有，他就像我的兄弟一样。他从来没那样看过我。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:216
translate chinese connie15_42e3bab3:

    # con "Nobody ever really looks at me like that."
    con "其实从来没人那样看过我。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:219
translate chinese connie15_bab07018:

    # pc "I don't see why not. You're a good looking woman."
    pc "我不明白为什么。你是个漂亮的女人。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:220
translate chinese connie15_2a7d9ea2:

    # con "I try, but nobody is interested in an old lady."
    con "我试过，但没人对一个老太太感兴趣。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:221
translate chinese connie15_f0f40b8d:

    # con "You got to use it while you're young, you know? Else you end up stuck in an old body, all alone."
    con "你知道吗，得趁年轻时好好利用它。否则最后就困在老迈的身体里，孤零零地一个人。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:222
translate chinese connie15_007fbff2:

    # pc "You have regrets?"
    pc "你有遗憾吗？"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:223
translate chinese connie15_79491ffd:

    # con "Oh, no. Not really."
    con "哦，没有。真的没有。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:224
translate chinese connie15_bf42fbfd:

    # con "My husband was good to me. We had a lot of really good years."
    con "我丈夫对我很好。我们度过了许多美好的岁月。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:227
translate chinese connie15_8fb15acf:

    # con "And that man was just as gifted as you are in bed."
    con "而且那男人在床上和你一样有天赋。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:228
translate chinese connie15_acf7a854:

    # con "God, I miss him."
    con "天啊，我好想他。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:231
translate chinese connie15_25ac1736:

    # pc "Did you have any children?"
    pc "你有孩子吗？"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:232
translate chinese connie15_4575dead:

    # con "One. A boy. Chase."
    con "一个。是个男孩。叫蔡斯。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:233
translate chinese connie15_5b0fb844:

    # con "He died over in Afghanistan."
    con "他在阿富汗阵亡了。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:234
translate chinese connie15_6c6d9416_1:

    # pc "Oh, I'm sorry."
    pc "哦，真抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:237
translate chinese connie15_0fa6aba4_1:

    # con "It's okay."
    con "没关系。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:238
translate chinese connie15_d075efd8:

    # con "Sometimes I feel like I died too..."
    con "有时我觉得自己好像也死了……"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:239
translate chinese connie15_454cba6d:

    # con "... and I'm just stuck here, waiting for my turn to go meet them."
    con "……只是被困在这里，等着轮到我去见他们。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:242
translate chinese connie15_19979052:

    # con "Thank you for making me feel alive for a little while."
    con "谢谢你让我感觉自己活了一会儿。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:243
translate chinese connie15_2911487b:

    # con "You're a good kid."
    con "你是个好孩子。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:246
translate chinese connie15_109a5d63:

    # con "I think you and Brandi make a very nice couple."
    con "我觉得你和布兰迪很般配。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:247
translate chinese connie15_68f01008:

    # con "You should consider settling down with her."
    con "你应该考虑和她安定下来。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:248
translate chinese connie15_19e05b84:

    # con "I see you coming into Jackson's with different girls."
    con "我看到你带着不同的女孩来杰克逊酒吧。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:249
translate chinese connie15_fedfc4a9:

    # con "You're young. That's a good thing. Experiment."
    con "你还年轻。这是件好事。 去尝试吧。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:250
translate chinese connie15_ec119d97:

    # con "But eventually, I hope you'll pick a girl and start a life and a family with her."
    con "但最终，我希望你能选定一个女孩，和她一起开始新生活，组建家庭。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:251
translate chinese connie15_1dc28a58:

    # con "And I hope you'll make each other very happy."
    con "也希望你们能让彼此非常幸福。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:252
translate chinese connie15_a40b7cd5:

    # pc "Thanks, Connie."
    pc "谢谢你，康妮。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:253
translate chinese connie15_0fd31492:

    # con "All right, that's enough reminiscing. Time to get dressed."
    con "好了，回忆到此为止。该穿衣服了。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:256
translate chinese connie15_2f1120e6:

    # "Before I leave, she hands me a tin full of chocolate chip cookies."
    "在我离开前，她递给我一罐巧克力曲奇。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:257
translate chinese connie15_189fa119:

    # con "I made these for Jackson, but he can have the next batch. You enjoy. You earned them."
    con "这些是给杰克逊做的，不过下一批他可以吃。你尽管享用吧。你配得上这些。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:258
translate chinese connie15_25e0f073:

    # con "Thanks again for making my day."
    con "再次感谢你让我今天过得这么开心。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:259
translate chinese connie15_a351accf:

    # con "I don't think we'll do this again, but I'm glad to have spent some time with you."
    con "我想我们应该不会再这样了，但很高兴能和你共度这段时光。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:260
translate chinese connie15_a9da76fd:

    # pc "Me too, Connie."
    pc "我也是，康妮。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:261
translate chinese connie15_c6512378:

    # con "You take care."
    con "你保重。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:264
translate chinese connie15_18c0b69c:

    # "I leave Connie's house and drive away."
    "我离开康妮的家，开车离去。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:265
translate chinese connie15_313c822e:

    # "I hope she'll be okay. She's a sweet lady."
    "希望她一切安好。她是个可爱的女士。"

# game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:266
translate chinese connie15_f74a794a:

    # "And she gives a killer gummer."
    "而且她那湿吻简直要命。"

translate chinese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:39
    old "Um... okay"
    new "嗯……好吧"

    # game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:55
    old "Age is just a number, baby"
    new "年龄只是个数字，宝贝"

    # game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:60
    old "Thanks, Connie"
    new "谢谢，康妮"

    # game/Scenes/Connie/connie15.rpy:72
    old "I wouldn't mind a piece of you"
    new "我倒是不介意来一发"

